<p>~/.zshrc</p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>ZSH_THEME=agnoster
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>

<p>После обновления .zshrc надо в терминале ввести:</p>
<div class="language-bash highlighter-coderay"><div class="CodeRay">
  <div class="code"><pre><span class="line-numbers"><a href="#n1" name="n1">1</a></span>source ~/.zshrc
</pre></div>
</div>
